1. Gather all pizza order methods by type for all available pizza establishments (web, phone, etc)
2. From a list of available pizza establishments, select the establishment to order from
3. From the selected pizza establishment select an available order method 
4. From available menu options concatenate a list of ordered items selected by the user and a given price
5. Submit the list of ordered items by the selected order method and confirm this submission with the pizza provider
6. Transact payment with the pizza provider and confirm delivery
7. Await pizza delivery based on confirmed timeframe
8. If the pizza is not delivered within the confirmed timeframe use the contact information from our order to contact the pizza provider
9. If the pizza provider withholds the pizza intentionally, initiate revenge protocols